:
    dcterms:title            "Information technology - City data model - Part 1: Foundation level concepts" ;
    dcterms:alternative      "City Data Model - Part 1: Foundation Level Concepts" ;
    skos:definition          "This ontology specifies the foundation-level concepts of the city data model." ;
    vann:preferredNamespaceUri "https://w3id.org/citydata/part1/v1/" ;
    vann:preferredNamespacePrefix "cdm1" ;
    :mainModule              true ;
    dcterms:creator          "Kenneth Vaughn" ;
    dcterms:creator          "Mark Fox" ;
    dcterms:creator          "Megan Katsumi" ;
    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "ISO/IEC 5087-1:2023" ;
    rdfs:seeAlso             <https://www.iso.org/standard/80718.html> ;
    rdfs:comment             "It is expected that the w3id.org domain will be updated to reference a JTC4 designated domain once the new JTC holds its first meeting. The updated ontology IRIs only include a major version number while the minor version number and patch number (jointly called the release number) are added in the version IRI. This provides stability of the concept IRIs as long as there are no changes that break backwards compatibility." ;
    rdfs:comment             "The prior version of this ontology used a different ontology IRI. This update remains semantically consistent with the version adopted as ISO 5087-1:2023." ;
